The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, orchid
1. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Flower   | marigold         | orchid    |

