.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, electrician
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, march
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
3. the electrician is the person who's birthday is in may##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | electrician | coach    |
| Birthday   | may       | march |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Sport         | climbing    | soccer   |

